Name: Crudely-Crafted Hollow Zero Investigator's ID
Desc: An ID card for a Hollow Zero Investigator.
Desc2:
Cardholder: Parker.
The card has been crudely made, with obvious ghosting on both the name and serial number. It also feels rough around the edges.
The outer laminate has scratches and tears in it, and it looks like it was discarded long ago.
